data.description: This Unique find will not last. This move in ready 2 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage plus pull thru work shop area, Screened in POOL home is a MUST see ! NEW ROOF March 2022, New A/C and duct work 2022, New Flooring thru out, Recently Painted exterior of home and concrete driveway. Large fenced in yard with concrete patio pad. This home is on a dead end street conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, grocery stores and more.  Just a 15-20 minute drive to access the Gulf, in Crystal River, or the Rainbow Springs, in Dunnellon for your kayaking, fishing and boating pleasure! Please note Pool to be Serviced and cleaned this weekend !
